com.bluegosling.function

Interface ShortUnaryOperator

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ShortUnaryOperator
    Represents an operation on a single short-valued operand that produces a short-valued result. This is the primitive type specialization of UnaryOperator for short.
    See Also:
    UnaryOperator
